responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "833C3F2F444CABB2C5B526B77DFC7673", "This isn\'t too complex, even though I\'m out of practice. It translates to, \'Gravehide strong and always ready. The Master promises big rewards soon. I need to meet the eye people at the old camp, north of Carphin, by the crumbled bridge. Stay hidden and wait for the sign.\' It ends lacking any signature, likely to obscure the author. It doesn\'t take a Lord Archon of the academy to see that this is a message to the goblins of the Gravehide tribe.")
name: DD_CSQ_0071_Monroe_20
